SYSJUNK: conf file update manager
Options
	Update Repo:
		-u => copy current conf files into local_repo and sync with master
	Install Configs:
		-i => sync local repo to master and copy conf files from local_repo to appropiate locations
	Add Config:
		-a => add a conf file to sysjunk
	Remove Config:
		-r => remove a conf file from sysjunk
	List Configs:
		-l => list conf files tracked by sysjunk
	Help:
		-h, -help, --help => print this manual page
